----------------------------------
USER VISIBLE CHANGES


OTHER CHANGES
The order in which the minimal representation of Omega and Simga
is stored internally within PopPredModel is changed from
row-major to column-major.  This change is not visible to the MDA users.

The job drivers generated by SPK Compiler have become more generic
so that the code for data simulation is embedded even when it is not
requested by the user and can be executed by flipping a boolean flag
within the job driver.

